    "review": {
      "title": "Stackable Sage",
      "text": "After extensive analysis involving one squinted eye and a mild headache, we present this review. Themed \"Tiny Dragon\", this sculpture contains 42 cubes. A tasteful number of cubes. Neither too few nor so many we had to sit down. A sensible height — neither scraping the sky nor hugging the floor awkwardly. Monochromatic. Bold. Either very intentional or the builder forgot there were other colors. In conclusion: 10/10, would be confused by again."
    },
