      "text": "This creation was clearly built with passion, or at least a vague sense of direction. Themed \"A Bridge to Nowhere Important\", this sculpture contains 64 cubes. A respectable cube count that suggests genuine effort or productive procrastination. A sensible height — neither scraping the sky nor hugging the floor awkwardly. A curated palette. The builder showed restraint, which frankly is impressive. Whatever it means, it means it loudly."
